### 1. 尝试预订 1 号滑板车 (成功路径)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/place
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "scooterId": 1,
  "totalCost": 15.50
}

### 2. 再次预订同编号滑板车 (应该失败，因为1号车已经被占用)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/place
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "scooterId": 1,
  "totalCost": 10.00
}

### 3. 查看 1 号用户的预订记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/user/1

### 4. 取消 1 号订单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/cancel/1

### 模拟支付部分 1. 先下一单 (此时状态会是 pending)

POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/place
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "scooterId": 1,
  "totalCost": 20.00
}

### 2. 模拟支付 (订单 ID 假设是刚才产生的那个)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/pay/1?cardNumber=1234567890


### F19: 管理员查看周收入统计 (Admin Revenue Stats)
### 只有在至少有一单是 'paid' 状态且在 7 天内时，这里才会有数据哦！
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/admin/revenue